WEBVTT

00:48.965 --> 00:51.134
EPISODE 2

01:30.924 --> 01:31.800
Look at her go.

01:48.066 --> 01:49.150
Why is he calling?

01:58.451 --> 01:59.994
Why aren't you picking up?

02:03.498 --> 02:04.541
Oh, my.

02:18.763 --> 02:20.056
I think he saw everything.

02:29.149 --> 02:30.191
What are you doing here?

02:31.359 --> 02:32.694
Why didn't you pick up?

02:33.361 --> 02:34.821
Because I was working.

02:34.904 --> 02:36.322
You mean you were dancing.

02:37.198 --> 02:38.533
I was working before that!

02:40.910 --> 02:43.037
Why are you here?
You said you were going to a club.

02:43.121 --> 02:44.205
I am at a club.

02:44.330 --> 02:46.249
I heard a club opened on the 12th floor.

02:46.332 --> 02:47.834
It's not so hot, though.

02:54.841 --> 02:57.844
- Mr. Nam!
- I love you, Mr. Nam!

03:06.269 --> 03:07.478
Cheers.

03:14.110 --> 03:17.530
What's wrong with my age?

03:18.489 --> 03:22.118
Love doesn't have an age limit

03:22.201 --> 03:23.578
- It doesn't!
- No!

03:24.913 --> 03:28.333
Same heart

03:28.416 --> 03:31.711
Same feeling

03:32.462 --> 03:38.468
You are the only one I love

03:39.010 --> 03:42.764
It's making me cry

03:42.847 --> 03:46.309
What's wrong with my age?

03:46.851 --> 03:51.022
It's the perfect age to fall in love

03:52.982 --> 03:54.400
This is my song.

03:54.525 --> 03:56.152
Get out of my way.

04:05.078 --> 04:10.375
I walked into the wind

04:11.501 --> 04:16.297
To that coffee shop early in the morning

04:40.947 --> 04:42.615
I barely managed to sneak out.

04:42.949 --> 04:44.450
You're still working, right?

04:48.705 --> 04:51.457
I'm almost done. Don't worry and go home.

04:51.541 --> 04:52.417
Thanks.

05:00.008 --> 05:02.385
Doing it like this saves so much time.

05:02.552 --> 05:04.595
No wonder it took me so long.

05:04.846 --> 05:07.932
I always did everything one by one
and made no progress.

05:08.016 --> 05:10.226
Right? This is why

05:10.852 --> 05:11.978
you should use your brain.

05:13.688 --> 05:14.772
Is that so?

05:16.649 --> 05:20.194
I think I just got hit by a rock.
I can't breathe.

05:20.695 --> 05:22.363
That mouth of yours.

05:25.074 --> 05:25.992
Stop following me.

05:28.077 --> 05:28.953
Hey!

05:29.412 --> 05:30.955
Wait until I catch you.

05:57.648 --> 05:58.649
Hold on.

05:58.983 --> 06:00.026
It hurts.

06:01.986 --> 06:03.696
- Ms. Yoon.
- Oh, gosh.

06:05.531 --> 06:08.117
- Ms. Yoon?
- Hey.

06:08.326 --> 06:09.452
- Ms. Yoon!
- Ye-eun.

06:09.535 --> 06:11.579
- You're still here!
- Yes.

06:12.080 --> 06:13.206
Ms. Yoon.

06:13.289 --> 06:16.000
- Why did you come back?
- I figured you'd still be here.

06:16.084 --> 06:18.503
- I thought you'd still be working alone.
- Well, yes.

06:19.170 --> 06:21.923
I'm almost done.
It's messy over there, so sit here.

06:22.006 --> 06:23.132
I'll help you.

06:23.216 --> 06:24.467
Let's chat as we wrap up.

06:24.550 --> 06:27.053
No, there's no need for that.

06:27.261 --> 06:29.013
We can wrap up tomorrow.

06:35.103 --> 06:36.104
What's wrong?

06:37.522 --> 06:39.315
He gave you a hard time, didn't he?

06:42.360 --> 06:45.404
It was so annoying. He kept touching me.

06:45.738 --> 06:48.199
I was so creeped out by him.

06:49.158 --> 06:51.577
It's my fault
for leaving you behind by yourself.

06:51.953 --> 06:53.621
It would've been worse if you were there.

06:53.996 --> 06:57.959
Mr. Kong doesn't know when to stop
because you don't tell him off.

06:59.961 --> 07:01.546
I'll cover for you next time.

07:01.629 --> 07:03.548
Just forget about tonight.

07:03.631 --> 07:06.300
You need to stop letting him off the hook.

07:06.384 --> 07:09.387
He keeps making fun of you
about your recent breakup.

07:09.720 --> 07:13.057
Why don't you say anything?
If I were you, I would've said something.

07:13.266 --> 07:15.935
I mean, come on.
You're obviously heartbroken.

07:16.018 --> 07:17.353
You liked him so much.

07:17.437 --> 07:18.563
I did not.

07:21.649 --> 07:22.817
Well...

07:24.235 --> 07:25.236
I mean...

07:26.237 --> 07:29.198
Liking someone a lot can be...

07:29.282 --> 07:31.409
When a man and a woman
are in a relationship,

07:31.492 --> 07:33.202
there are good times and...

07:33.453 --> 07:34.704
- You know.
- That's true.

07:34.787 --> 07:37.540
What I meant to say
is that you used to love him

07:37.623 --> 07:41.210
- so much that--
- I think you're way too drunk.

07:41.294 --> 07:42.462
- No, I'm not.
- Stand up.

07:42.545 --> 07:44.714
- Do you think you can find your way home?
- Of course.

07:44.797 --> 07:46.215
- Okay.
- But Ms. Yoon, I can help--

07:46.299 --> 07:47.300
Will you be okay?

07:47.383 --> 07:49.177
- I'll go home after--
- Here. Let's go.

07:49.260 --> 07:52.221
Don't go anywhere. Face this way.

07:52.472 --> 07:54.015
I'll go get my purse.

07:55.558 --> 07:57.477
Don't you have to finish that by yourself?

07:57.560 --> 07:59.395
- I can help you.
- No, that's okay. It's fine.

07:59.479 --> 08:01.564
I'll just finish the rest tomorrow.

08:01.647 --> 08:03.649
Ms. Yoon, I'll turn the lights off.

08:03.733 --> 08:06.694
No, I'll... I'll turn them off. Wait.

08:07.403 --> 08:08.488
- Gosh.
- The lights.

08:08.571 --> 08:11.157
Do we have to turn the lights off?

08:12.950 --> 08:14.243
Gosh, my back.

08:27.798 --> 08:28.758
Done!

08:29.217 --> 08:30.301
Come on.

08:32.220 --> 08:33.721
Let's go.

08:36.516 --> 08:37.767
- Be careful.
- I'm fine.

08:37.850 --> 08:39.352
Get a hold of yourself.

08:40.102 --> 08:42.730
- I'll call a taxi.
- No, I'll do it. Let me do it.

08:43.731 --> 08:46.609
- I need one, too.
- I need to stop by somewhere.

08:46.692 --> 08:48.319
I need to go to my friend's store.

08:48.402 --> 08:49.779
Oh, that place.

08:50.321 --> 08:51.781
The name of the owner was...

08:52.073 --> 08:54.283
- Seo Gyeong-seon.
- Yes, that's right.

08:54.742 --> 08:56.827
You must be really close with her.

08:56.911 --> 08:58.037
You could say that.

08:58.371 --> 09:00.623
I'm calling from DMC, Sangam-dong.

09:01.332 --> 09:02.542
One taxi for Yeongdeungpo.

09:03.834 --> 09:06.379
- And another one for...
- It's so cold.

09:07.213 --> 09:10.258
I'll call you back later. Thank you.

09:10.550 --> 09:12.760
- Is it coming?
- Yes, let's go.

09:12.843 --> 09:14.428
- Ms. Yoon.
- Be careful.

09:14.512 --> 09:17.348
- You need to sober up.
- I like you so much.

09:17.431 --> 09:21.060
- You know that, right?
- I like you a lot as well.

09:27.775 --> 09:29.902
Gosh, what am I supposed to do?

09:36.534 --> 09:39.328
- Let's get you home.
- Wait. Ms. Yoon.

09:39.412 --> 09:40.580
Yes? What is it?

09:40.663 --> 09:42.498
I'm going to become just like you,

09:42.582 --> 09:46.460
- a cool career-oriented woman.
- That's great. I hope you do.

09:46.544 --> 09:47.753
- Let's go.
- But go home first.

09:47.837 --> 09:51.465
Wait a minute. Wait.
Why do you keep trying to send me home?

09:51.591 --> 09:53.175
I like being with you.

09:53.259 --> 09:54.635
The driver's been waiting for you.

09:54.719 --> 09:56.637
- You must not like me.
- Let's get going.

09:56.721 --> 09:59.348
I like you a lot,
but you need to go home for now.

09:59.432 --> 10:01.726
- Let's get you inside. Good.
- Wait.

10:03.269 --> 10:04.145
You can--

10:04.270 --> 10:06.897
Ms. Yoon, I love you.

10:06.981 --> 10:09.567
I love you too. Get inside.

10:10.234 --> 10:11.444
You can go now.

10:12.570 --> 10:14.363
Bye, Ms. Yoon!

11:05.873 --> 11:06.874
Jun-hui.

11:07.958 --> 11:09.752
Hey, where are you?

11:12.922 --> 11:14.465
Where did he go?

11:17.802 --> 11:18.803
Jun-hui.

11:28.020 --> 11:29.897
What took you so long?

11:31.482 --> 11:33.692
I tried my best to hurry up.

11:34.527 --> 11:37.613
Don't lie. I could've crawled over here
faster than you.

11:51.627 --> 11:52.878
I got home safely.

11:53.546 --> 11:54.922
Good night.

11:57.633 --> 11:59.760
GOOD...

12:01.053 --> 12:02.388
Good night.

12:32.751 --> 12:34.962
Are you coming home or leaving?

12:35.129 --> 12:37.047
Can't you tell? I'm going to work.

12:37.465 --> 12:40.134
I can't tell because you rarely come home.

12:41.469 --> 12:44.889
Why can't you show some support
for your brother who works all night?

12:45.639 --> 12:48.601
How am I supposed to know
if you worked or partied?

12:48.684 --> 12:49.894
I did half of each.

12:51.604 --> 12:52.438
My goodness.

12:56.567 --> 12:59.028
You're never even home.
It's a waste of rent.

12:59.528 --> 13:02.573
Why don't you live with me
so that you can save money?

13:04.116 --> 13:04.992
Are you crazy?

13:05.993 --> 13:07.119
Why would you say that?

13:07.786 --> 13:11.081
Let's respect each other's privacy
even though we're siblings.

13:12.416 --> 13:13.709
Do you have a girl?

13:13.834 --> 13:14.835
A girl?

13:15.419 --> 13:16.670
Which one are you talking about?

13:18.756 --> 13:19.757
We'll crash.

13:20.090 --> 13:22.092
Traffic accidents
aren't the only accidents.

13:22.176 --> 13:23.761
Do you have any idea how startled I was

13:23.844 --> 13:26.680
when you were playing Jin-a's boyfriend
over the phone?

13:27.181 --> 13:30.017
I thought you were fighting
with some guy over a girl.

13:30.142 --> 13:32.269
You can't imagine how nervous I was.

13:33.020 --> 13:34.438
I would easily beat any guy.

13:34.855 --> 13:36.315
Listen to me carefully.

13:36.982 --> 13:38.901
If you ever bring home
a rude, inconsiderate bitch

13:38.984 --> 13:40.611
as your future wife,

13:40.694 --> 13:42.446
I'll kill both of you.

13:43.155 --> 13:45.115
But what if she's really pretty?

13:46.033 --> 13:48.536
If she's prettier than I am,

13:48.619 --> 13:49.828
I'll think about it.

13:51.413 --> 13:53.666
I think what you just said
made my hearing go bad.

13:56.460 --> 13:57.795
Okay, I'm sorry.

13:58.879 --> 14:00.381
My gosh.

14:02.967 --> 14:05.135
Ms. Yoon, come here.

14:13.185 --> 14:15.771
Do you call this a report

14:15.896 --> 14:17.356
or a drawing?

14:18.524 --> 14:20.985
I did try to make it good.
Do you not like it?

14:23.070 --> 14:25.197
Ms. Geum, bring me a ruler.

14:33.497 --> 14:34.540
Stay there.

14:36.000 --> 14:37.668
Does this look aligned to you?

14:38.002 --> 14:40.462
I put an indentation
because it is a new paragraph.

14:40.546 --> 14:41.714
Are you a novelist?

14:42.548 --> 14:44.550
Don't waste time on useless things.

14:44.633 --> 14:46.969
Focus on the purpose of the report.

14:47.344 --> 14:48.304
Stay there.

14:53.225 --> 14:57.062
This is what you came up with
for the presentation?

15:01.650 --> 15:02.943
That is the template

15:03.027 --> 15:05.237
that was most frequently used
for the past three years.

15:05.529 --> 15:06.864
Who told you to plagiarize?

15:07.948 --> 15:09.950
You have to be creative.

15:10.200 --> 15:13.495
You changed the numbers and figures
on what's already there.

15:13.579 --> 15:14.622
What do you call that?

15:14.705 --> 15:17.499
All you did was cut and paste.

15:18.250 --> 15:20.002
It's actually "copy and paste," sir.

15:23.797 --> 15:26.842
If you're so smart,
why is your report so flimsy?

15:27.635 --> 15:28.928
Do it all over.

15:29.261 --> 15:30.846
Make it more creative and innovative.

15:31.430 --> 15:32.431
Stay there.

15:33.098 --> 15:34.558
Ms. Kang, get over here.

15:47.196 --> 15:48.530
About yesterday...

15:49.490 --> 15:52.034
Even our youngest members
like Dong-u and Ye-eun

15:52.117 --> 15:54.203
stayed until the end of our team dinner.

15:54.995 --> 15:58.749
But you seniors sneaked out
when you should be setting an example.

15:59.833 --> 16:01.001
Why do we have team dinners?

16:01.543 --> 16:04.254
The aim is to increase employee devotion
and build teamwork.

16:05.673 --> 16:06.882
You should know better.

16:08.050 --> 16:11.512
I consider those who fail
to be team players very inconsiderate.

16:12.012 --> 16:13.764
Where's your sense of camaraderie?

16:14.306 --> 16:16.016
Think about it.

16:16.767 --> 16:18.602
We don't tolerate sexual discrimination.

16:18.686 --> 16:22.940
And it's not like
anybody forces you to drink.

16:23.023 --> 16:26.068
We just get along as equal human beings.

16:27.194 --> 16:28.988
What's wrong with you people?

16:30.781 --> 16:31.907
Dismissed!

16:34.034 --> 16:35.202
Take this with you!

16:45.629 --> 16:46.714
Let's grab something to eat.

16:46.797 --> 16:49.049
Let's go. Dong-u, hurry up.

16:49.133 --> 16:49.967
Yes, sir.

16:56.223 --> 16:59.643
If I can sit behind a desk all day
like those guys,

16:59.727 --> 17:01.103
I will attend every team dinner.

17:01.729 --> 17:03.647
There isn't enough manpower
to support new stores.

17:03.731 --> 17:04.815
I work around the clock.

17:04.898 --> 17:07.359
I don't have the energy
to sit through those dinners.

17:08.193 --> 17:09.653
Tell me about it.

17:09.987 --> 17:12.740
It's getting harder
to wake up in the morning.

17:12.823 --> 17:13.991
I must be getting old.

17:14.074 --> 17:15.784
What's wrong with you two?

17:16.744 --> 17:18.245
We're still in the game.

17:18.328 --> 17:21.248
It's easy for you to say that
because you are younger than me.

17:22.666 --> 17:24.168
Enough with the age talk.

17:24.293 --> 17:25.919
Do you want me to use honorifics to you?

17:26.003 --> 17:27.254
Feel free to do that.

17:27.838 --> 17:31.633
No matter how young or old you are,
you need your strength.

17:31.717 --> 17:33.385
- Let's eat something healthy.
- Sounds good.

17:34.762 --> 17:35.637
Pho.

17:36.805 --> 17:37.681
What?

17:37.890 --> 17:39.391
Pho isn't healthy.

17:40.184 --> 17:41.977
It is if you enjoy it.

17:42.728 --> 17:43.729
Let's go.

17:44.855 --> 17:46.148
Thank you.

17:47.316 --> 17:48.817
Enjoy.

17:49.068 --> 17:49.985
Hey.

17:50.611 --> 17:52.738
Set me up with her. I beg you.

17:52.821 --> 17:53.781
Welcome.

17:53.864 --> 17:56.700
Every night,
your buddy is suffering from loneliness...

17:57.785 --> 17:59.953
- Hello.
- Hey, Jin-a.

18:01.789 --> 18:03.123
I didn't expect to see you here.

18:03.707 --> 18:04.958
Please take a seat.

18:26.855 --> 18:27.773
Where do you live?

18:32.444 --> 18:33.737
Me?

18:33.821 --> 18:35.906
My parents live in the countryside.

18:35.989 --> 18:37.741
I live in Mok-dong.

18:39.409 --> 18:40.327
I live alone.

18:41.036 --> 18:43.789
Awesome. No, that came out wrong.

18:44.373 --> 18:46.333
I mean, you live in an awesome area.

18:48.794 --> 18:51.213
- Where do you live?
- I live in Bundang.

18:51.296 --> 18:52.756
I live in Bangbae-dong.

18:53.715 --> 18:54.883
Please excuse me.

18:55.384 --> 18:56.844
Enjoy your meal.

18:58.137 --> 18:59.179
See you.

19:05.269 --> 19:07.896
Can you pay for the food?
I helped you yesterday.

19:09.481 --> 19:10.691
Be quiet.

19:11.024 --> 19:11.859
Thanks.

19:14.736 --> 19:18.323
How do you two know each other?

19:20.659 --> 19:23.203
I transferred when I was in second grade.

19:23.370 --> 19:24.705
That's over 20 years ago.

19:25.455 --> 19:26.498
You're right.

19:26.707 --> 19:28.917
His sister and I went to the same school
until college.

19:31.837 --> 19:33.714
You're basically family.

19:34.798 --> 19:35.757
Don't you know?

19:35.841 --> 19:37.384
My sister owns one of your stores.

19:39.678 --> 19:40.596
Really?

19:41.763 --> 19:42.806
Which one?

19:44.808 --> 19:46.018
Which store is it?

19:56.111 --> 19:57.779
I thought you already left.

19:59.865 --> 20:01.783
Why? Is something wrong?

20:02.326 --> 20:05.287
You're in charge of Ms. Seo's store.

20:05.746 --> 20:07.080
I'll take that store from now on.

20:08.081 --> 20:09.750
I don't think that's a good idea.

20:09.833 --> 20:12.169
My friend would be disappointed.

20:13.212 --> 20:15.005
I won't disappoint her.

20:15.255 --> 20:17.341
You took the Gasan store from me too.

20:17.966 --> 20:21.345
That's because you had trouble
with the owner there.

20:21.428 --> 20:23.180
This is a different case.

20:24.932 --> 20:26.183
Is that a no?

20:26.266 --> 20:28.185
No, it's not that.

20:28.268 --> 20:30.854
I'm saying you could put me
in a difficult position.

20:32.064 --> 20:33.357
Okay, fine.

20:34.107 --> 20:35.317
I'll take care of it.

20:45.160 --> 20:49.081
Why did he tell her
that his sister owns a store?

20:49.373 --> 20:51.541
Aren't there better things to talk about?

20:53.460 --> 20:55.212
Ms. Yoon, who are you talking to?

20:56.296 --> 20:58.882
I was talking nonsense. Bye.

21:27.661 --> 21:28.912
What did you get?

21:28.996 --> 21:31.665
Go through that later
and get me some water.

21:31.999 --> 21:33.166
I'm sweating.

21:33.625 --> 21:35.043
Is it hot outside?

21:35.377 --> 21:37.212
It's because I'm frustrated.

21:56.606 --> 21:58.900
We will go bankrupt
for getting wedding gifts.

22:00.152 --> 22:01.653
It's our little nephew's.

22:02.696 --> 22:05.615
My brother and his wife seem to like
the new daughter-in-law.

22:07.075 --> 22:09.244
She was bragging so much,

22:09.328 --> 22:11.663
so I thought the daughter-in-law
had an amazing background.

22:11.913 --> 22:13.040
The only thing to brag about

22:13.123 --> 22:15.375
was that her father
was district representative.

22:15.459 --> 22:17.711
- That is quite something.
- That is nothing to brag about.

22:19.671 --> 22:21.631
This one must be from your friend.

22:22.716 --> 22:25.510
The second daughter of my friend
who lives in Seocho-dong.

22:27.054 --> 22:30.265
The new in-laws are a family
of a former bank president.

22:30.348 --> 22:32.684
They must be influential
in the financial circle.

22:33.018 --> 22:35.395
She brags about them all the time.

22:35.479 --> 22:37.981
Whenever someone seems envious of Jin-a,

22:38.648 --> 22:40.734
she talks about her future in-laws

22:40.901 --> 22:43.153
and how powerful they are.

22:44.362 --> 22:45.989
I mean, I can't blame her.

22:46.239 --> 22:49.326
They did sound like a prestigious family.

22:49.409 --> 22:51.495
Let's hope the same for Jin-a.

22:51.995 --> 22:54.289
That's what I'm worried about.

22:54.498 --> 22:57.667
If we leave it to Jin-a,
she'll take forever to get married.

22:58.835 --> 23:01.254
You should sit Gyu-min down

23:01.338 --> 23:02.672
and talk to him.

23:03.340 --> 23:05.342
- I should?
- We have to marry Jin-a off.

23:05.634 --> 23:08.011
When will we hold a wedding ceremony
of our own child?

23:08.595 --> 23:09.596
Okay.

23:10.097 --> 23:14.101
Can you please take it more seriously?

23:14.559 --> 23:17.062
- Come on.
- I get it.

23:19.314 --> 23:20.732
You'd better talk to him

23:21.733 --> 23:23.068
or you're not getting any meals.

23:35.455 --> 23:36.414
What is it?

23:36.623 --> 23:38.750
Do you not like this place?
Shall we go somewhere else?

23:39.751 --> 23:41.044
Have you been here before?

23:42.045 --> 23:44.548
For a company dinner a long time ago.
It was pretty good.

23:44.631 --> 23:45.841
We can go somewhere else.

23:47.509 --> 23:48.635
It's fine.

23:55.559 --> 23:57.727
Welcome back. This way please.

24:00.522 --> 24:03.024
The waiter must have
an exceptional memory.

24:10.240 --> 24:11.491
We can sit over there, right?

24:11.575 --> 24:13.160
Yes, as you please.

24:23.170 --> 24:24.296
Thank you.

24:35.265 --> 24:36.683
Is there anything you want to drink?

24:38.393 --> 24:39.811
What should we have?

24:41.813 --> 24:43.231
Something you tried before.

24:43.690 --> 24:46.067
- What?
- The one you recently had.

24:47.694 --> 24:49.404
I haven't been here recently.

24:58.413 --> 24:59.456
What is it?

25:00.707 --> 25:01.708
I'm going to the restroom.

25:02.417 --> 25:03.335
Okay.

25:04.127 --> 25:07.380
I wouldn't even want to be with him
for a single second.

25:07.756 --> 25:09.841
Why are you even listening to him?

25:10.508 --> 25:13.803
Just splash a glass of wine on him
and get out of there.

25:17.682 --> 25:20.185
You'll see how it goes? What do you mean?

25:20.727 --> 25:22.103
Are you going to see Gyu-min again?

25:23.396 --> 25:24.648
Then why...

25:24.731 --> 25:26.233
Why bother wasting time?

25:27.525 --> 25:29.444
You'd better not do anything stupid.

25:31.321 --> 25:32.322
Okay.

25:33.823 --> 25:35.075
Who was that?

25:35.450 --> 25:37.327
Who do you think? It was Jin-a.

25:37.494 --> 25:39.496
Apparently, Gyu-min showed up again.

25:40.205 --> 25:41.039
Why?

25:41.331 --> 25:43.750
Why do you think?
He wants to win her over somehow.

25:43.833 --> 25:45.585
Doesn't Jin-a know what he's trying to do?

25:46.086 --> 25:47.712
- Why does she keep meeting him?
- Exactly...

25:48.880 --> 25:50.757
She's not meeting him on her own will.

25:50.840 --> 25:52.592
He keeps showing up without notice.

25:52.676 --> 25:54.302
That's because she's soft on him.

25:54.386 --> 25:57.597
Hey, I'm sure she'll end it today.
I doubt she'll give him another...

25:58.348 --> 25:59.724
Sure.

26:01.601 --> 26:03.645
Why are you getting worked up over it?

26:05.355 --> 26:06.189
I'm not.

26:31.131 --> 26:33.550
I'm doing my best
to make things right between us.

26:34.801 --> 26:36.803
But you're making it really difficult.

26:38.805 --> 26:39.681
Is it difficult?

26:39.764 --> 26:42.100
Of course. I don't know what to do.

26:45.520 --> 26:48.189
Are you brazen or brainless?

26:50.567 --> 26:51.693
What?

26:52.152 --> 26:53.236
How could you bring me here?

26:55.071 --> 26:57.240
Aren't you trying to work things out
between us?

27:00.869 --> 27:03.788
The lipstick and stockings...

27:08.543 --> 27:09.544
What?

27:10.545 --> 27:11.880
Do you want to sue me?

27:13.381 --> 27:15.717
- Let's add assault on top of that.
- Jin-a.

27:18.553 --> 27:21.431
I came to end our relationship
on a good note.

27:24.351 --> 27:25.560
But you're so cruel.

27:27.145 --> 27:28.646
You're really the worst.

27:42.994 --> 27:44.537
I'm not the only at fault.

27:46.873 --> 27:49.209
Who is that guy you were with
the other day?

27:49.709 --> 27:51.544
- My gosh.
- See?

27:51.628 --> 27:54.631
You were seeing someone else, too.
Why are you making me the bad guy?

27:54.964 --> 27:56.925
Can't we just call it even?

27:57.717 --> 27:58.968
It wasn't you.

27:59.427 --> 28:02.263
It was me. I'm the one to blame
for having dated you.

28:03.306 --> 28:05.517
Hey, you can't just leave like that!

28:07.394 --> 28:09.646
What's wrong?
Do you need money for the valet again?

28:09.979 --> 28:12.399
No, you drank.
Should I pay for your chauffeur service?

28:26.871 --> 28:28.581
You seem upset.

28:29.999 --> 28:31.126
Hello.

28:31.334 --> 28:32.377
Hello.

28:33.378 --> 28:35.839
Your outfit is amazing today.

28:37.507 --> 28:38.675
Thank you.

28:39.884 --> 28:44.013
Jun-hui, you seem to be
in a bad mood today.

28:44.097 --> 28:46.433
Right? See?

28:46.725 --> 28:47.767
I'm fine.

28:54.858 --> 28:57.485
Did you say you live in Mok-dong?
Where exactly do you live?

28:58.737 --> 29:00.363
Five minutes away from the station.

29:00.488 --> 29:01.865
That's a good spot to live in.

29:01.948 --> 29:02.907
Yes, you're right.

29:04.784 --> 29:05.827
Hey.

29:06.578 --> 29:08.580
- Hello.
- Hello.

29:12.542 --> 29:13.918
The pizza place near the station...

29:15.003 --> 29:16.296
Do you know that place?

29:16.796 --> 29:18.590
Yes, that place was nice.

29:18.673 --> 29:20.717
There's a franchise store nearby.

29:20.800 --> 29:22.510
Oh, really? Where?

29:22.844 --> 29:26.139
Would you mind taking us there?

29:27.056 --> 29:28.600
Of course not.

29:29.392 --> 29:32.103
Why don't we just eat lunch there today?

29:32.854 --> 29:34.230
Do you have time?

29:34.314 --> 29:35.356
Yes, of course.

29:35.440 --> 29:37.484
If we don't, we'll make time.

29:37.817 --> 29:38.651
Why are you so eager?

29:38.735 --> 29:40.111
By the way,

29:41.446 --> 29:43.740
- can I have your number?
- Oh, mine? Okay.

29:50.413 --> 29:51.372
Do you want to come too?

29:53.124 --> 29:54.209
To where?

29:54.918 --> 29:57.754
I wasn't listening. I was busy texting.

30:00.965 --> 30:01.925
I'll see you.

30:02.884 --> 30:03.885
Bye.

30:04.928 --> 30:06.429
I'll text you later.

30:30.537 --> 30:31.621
So...

30:33.581 --> 30:34.582
You can stay seated.

30:40.421 --> 30:42.257
I came to tell you something
before the meeting.

30:42.423 --> 30:43.633
Did you watch yesterday's news?

30:46.469 --> 30:48.096
Of course, you didn't.

30:49.681 --> 30:52.308
The market size of the coffee industry

30:52.392 --> 30:53.893
reached 6.4 trillion won last year.

30:56.771 --> 30:58.731
Then how much do you think we make?

31:01.568 --> 31:03.611
I haven't heard anything
about opening a new store.

31:03.695 --> 31:04.863
Sales Team. No news?

31:05.697 --> 31:07.323
I'm sorry, sir. We'll work harder.

31:08.700 --> 31:11.244
I'm not saying that you don't need
to focus on our existing stores.

31:11.911 --> 31:13.621
There needs to be some progress.

31:13.788 --> 31:15.206
Customers don't just show up

31:15.498 --> 31:16.833
after we open a store.

31:18.835 --> 31:21.880
- What do you want?
- We noticed that a store isn't open yet.

31:21.963 --> 31:23.923
We can't get in touch with the owner.

31:24.007 --> 31:26.134
Look at the time. Why is it still closed?

31:27.135 --> 31:29.053
- Which store is it?
- The one in Gasan.

31:32.765 --> 31:35.727
If it doesn't open in 30 minutes,
you'll all get fired.

31:35.810 --> 31:37.186
Get moving!

31:44.235 --> 31:47.196
- Something urgent came up
- Hello, I was about to give you a call.

31:47.280 --> 31:49.073
- at one of our stores.
- I'm sorry.

31:49.157 --> 31:50.533
- Hello?
- Yes, that's right.

31:50.617 --> 31:51.868
Yes, Mr. Kong.

31:52.160 --> 31:54.621
- I'm on my way, sir.
- I'll call you. I'm sorry.

31:54.746 --> 31:56.539
- Bye.
- It says...

31:57.165 --> 31:59.167
- it'll take about 17 minutes.
- Hello.

31:59.250 --> 32:01.252
- Yes.
- This is Geum Bo-ra.

32:01.502 --> 32:03.046
- Yes, sir.
- I know we were planning

32:03.129 --> 32:05.840
- to have a meeting this morning.
- Yes, okay.

32:05.924 --> 32:07.592
- I'm afraid we'll have to cancel.
- Yes, sir.

32:08.801 --> 32:09.761
Yes, Mr. Kong.

32:11.137 --> 32:13.598
- Yes, sir.
- The head office is trying

32:13.681 --> 32:16.059
- to handle an urgent situation.
- We'll be there in 17 minutes.

32:16.726 --> 32:21.856
- Then can I call you when I'm done?
- Hi, Jun-hui. It's me, Se-yeong.

32:21.940 --> 32:25.902
- It's not that far from that place.
- Yes. I'm really sorry.

32:26.194 --> 32:28.029
Something urgent came up.

32:28.112 --> 32:30.114
I'm heading over to one of our stores.

32:31.783 --> 32:34.160
I'm sorry. I'm the one
who suggested eating together.

32:36.245 --> 32:38.623
You're making me feel even sorrier.

32:42.377 --> 32:46.130
I'll treat you to a nice meal
in a few days. Okay.

32:47.298 --> 32:48.633
Okay, let me know.

32:49.717 --> 32:52.595
I see. No, it's okay.

32:53.930 --> 32:55.765
We can eat together next time.

32:57.016 --> 32:58.142
Okay, bye.

32:59.769 --> 33:01.187
Next time? Call her again

33:01.270 --> 33:03.314
- and tell her that we have time tonight.
- Seriously...

33:03.940 --> 33:06.943
- She's busy. Why are you being so clingy?
- Clingy?

33:07.235 --> 33:10.071
I'm not being clingy.
I'm just being proactive.

33:10.822 --> 33:12.782
This is why you don't have a girlfriend.

33:15.159 --> 33:16.160
You have a long way to go.

33:16.911 --> 33:19.831
Let's see who you end up dating.

33:24.335 --> 33:27.046
I think he's doing this
because I sent a report about what he did.

33:27.130 --> 33:29.132
We have most of the ingredients.

33:29.298 --> 33:31.050
I'll ask the general manager
for what we need.

33:31.134 --> 33:32.260
Let's get in position first.

33:32.343 --> 33:33.636
I'll handle the cash register.

33:37.015 --> 33:38.599
Bo-ra, you're the best at making drinks.

33:38.683 --> 33:41.310
You are an SCA certificate holder.
No one's better than you at this.

33:41.394 --> 33:43.021
Are you complimenting me or forcing me?

33:43.521 --> 33:46.024
Mr. Kim and Ye-eun.
You guys can divide work together.

33:46.107 --> 33:48.609
Take care of this area.
One of you should cover the storage room.

33:48.693 --> 33:49.652
- Yes, ma'am.
- Yes, ma'am.

33:51.654 --> 33:53.072
- Follow me.
- Okay.

33:59.120 --> 34:00.788
- Hello.
- Hello.

34:02.707 --> 34:04.876
She was supposed to use
her own money for this.

34:04.959 --> 34:06.335
Why is it coming out of our pocket?

34:07.962 --> 34:11.257
Mr. Jo also told Jin-a
to take care of the mess she made.

34:12.508 --> 34:16.012
It wasn't her fault,
so I think it's unfair for her to pay.

34:16.637 --> 34:19.265
We already settled this case.

34:19.891 --> 34:21.684
What do you mean you think it's unfair?

34:22.226 --> 34:23.895
Who's going to take responsibility
for this?

34:24.395 --> 34:25.938
Someone needs to take care of this.

34:31.194 --> 34:33.196
Why are you looking at me like that?

34:34.280 --> 34:37.241
There are a lot of things
I've been lenient about

34:38.242 --> 34:39.452
these days.

34:44.665 --> 34:46.042
I'll rewrite the report, sir.

34:57.720 --> 34:59.722
She's very subtly arrogant.

35:01.057 --> 35:02.141
I'd better...

35:03.184 --> 35:04.811
teach her a lesson soon.

35:13.986 --> 35:15.029
Where's Mr. Nam?

35:16.030 --> 35:17.240
He's inside, sir.

35:19.534 --> 35:20.910
Were you looking for me, sir?

35:21.410 --> 35:23.454
Let's eat lunch together
if you don't have any plans.

35:23.955 --> 35:26.165
Sure. Let me go put on my shoes, sir.

35:28.501 --> 35:30.002
You should come too, Ms. Jeong.

35:30.294 --> 35:32.338
- I have some questions to ask.
- Yes, sir.

35:43.266 --> 35:45.101
How are things going
at the store in Gasan?

35:46.435 --> 35:47.270
Oh, well...

35:48.980 --> 35:52.275
I received a report saying

35:52.775 --> 35:54.193
that everything's going really well.

35:54.277 --> 35:56.904
Of course. They're all professionals.

35:58.322 --> 36:01.117
Jin-a was always at the top of her game.

36:01.200 --> 36:02.910
What's up with her lately?

36:03.911 --> 36:05.079
I know.

36:07.331 --> 36:12.211
You never really know a person
until they show their true colors.

36:13.921 --> 36:16.507
Who's the one who forgot to approve
the gifts for the opening event?

36:24.849 --> 36:27.185
I should have double checked.
I'm sorry, sir.

36:28.227 --> 36:30.396
Since when did you forget anything?

36:31.105 --> 36:33.774
I'll look into how it all happened
and report to you, sir.

36:36.402 --> 36:38.196
Investigate thoroughly.

36:49.832 --> 36:52.126
Ms. Jeong, give me a minute.

36:54.170 --> 36:55.213
Come here.

37:05.431 --> 37:06.515
Well...

37:07.225 --> 37:09.894
About what Mr. Jo asked you
to investigate...

37:10.144 --> 37:11.395
What are you going to do?

37:12.355 --> 37:15.316
As you instructed,
I'll make Jin-a pay for all the products

37:15.399 --> 37:17.026
and tell him the truth about the approval.

37:18.027 --> 37:19.195
The truth?

37:21.197 --> 37:23.574
The members of our team keep a photocopy

37:23.866 --> 37:26.285
of each approval form
to spot mistakes easily.

37:26.535 --> 37:30.498
And I noticed that everything was fine
until I approved it.

37:38.172 --> 37:40.258
I gave it some thought, you know.

37:42.260 --> 37:45.179
An assistant manager
can't afford to pay for all of that.

37:46.931 --> 37:48.266
A team dinner...

37:48.349 --> 37:52.061
I'll just think of it
as paying for a team dinner.

37:52.144 --> 37:53.271
That won't be too bad, right?

37:55.022 --> 37:57.191
The total cost of 100 lipsticks
is 2.1 million won,

37:57.275 --> 37:59.026
and that of 100 mobile coupons
is 320,000 won.

37:59.527 --> 38:02.071
That adds up to a total
of 2.42 million won, sir.

38:03.447 --> 38:04.448
Okay.

38:06.450 --> 38:07.660
I know how to add.

38:08.577 --> 38:09.829
I just wanted to check.

38:10.079 --> 38:11.497
Who's going to report it to Mr. Jo--

38:11.580 --> 38:12.957
I'll do it.

38:30.016 --> 38:32.643
Good work, everyone.

38:33.019 --> 38:35.104
I noticed
that we have quite good teamwork.

38:35.646 --> 38:37.606
I worked so hard
that I even broke my nails.

38:37.690 --> 38:39.275
You just pressed some buttons.

38:39.358 --> 38:40.609
My shoulders are killing me.

38:41.777 --> 38:42.945
What's happening tomorrow?

38:43.654 --> 38:45.698
I'll try talking to the owner.

38:45.948 --> 38:48.492
Some of us might have to work here again.

38:48.576 --> 38:51.287
I don't care about what happens.
I'm not coming tomorrow.

38:51.370 --> 38:53.247
- See you guys.
- Bye.

38:53.331 --> 38:55.249
- Bye.
- Thanks. Good work.

38:55.750 --> 38:57.084
It's our job after all.

38:57.918 --> 38:59.795
You'd better make it up to me personally.

39:01.297 --> 39:03.132
- Bye.
- Bye.

39:06.302 --> 39:07.970
You two should go home too.

39:08.054 --> 39:09.889
I need to take the car back to the office.

39:09.972 --> 39:12.516
I need to go visit the owner.
I'll return it after I use it.

39:12.975 --> 39:15.269
- Great work, you guys.
- Should I come with you?

39:15.394 --> 39:17.313
I already feel bad
for making you work here today.

39:17.396 --> 39:19.106
Go home and get some rest.

39:19.190 --> 39:20.399
- See you tomorrow.
- Bye.

39:20.483 --> 39:22.109
Good work.

39:28.532 --> 39:29.658
Gosh, my legs.

39:57.645 --> 40:01.440
Sir, avoiding me won't solve anything.

40:01.899 --> 40:03.150
Please call me.

41:44.877 --> 41:46.921
That asshole said
you were like this, right?

41:47.630 --> 41:48.714
"That asshole"?

41:51.175 --> 41:53.928
Should I address him with respect
since you're dating him again?

41:56.430 --> 41:57.640
What do you mean?

41:58.432 --> 42:01.018
Did Gyeong-seon tell you that?
Did she say I'm seeing him again?

42:03.521 --> 42:06.148
No, I just figured it'd be hard
for you to end it with him

42:06.232 --> 42:07.733
since you two used to be madly in love.

42:09.443 --> 42:10.861
"Madly in love"?

42:11.820 --> 42:13.614
What's your problem?

42:13.906 --> 42:15.866
Why would you jump to conclusions?

42:18.160 --> 42:19.745
I heard about everything, okay?

42:20.496 --> 42:22.122
You two must have been quite the couple.

42:22.206 --> 42:23.332
Even your junior pities you.

42:23.415 --> 42:26.418
Haven't you ever been like that
when you are in a relationship?

42:26.752 --> 42:27.836
You need to be passionate.

42:28.462 --> 42:30.422
If you were never passionate,
you're the weird one.

42:30.548 --> 42:33.133
That only means that you have no respect
for the other person.

42:34.885 --> 42:36.679
It's only natural

42:36.762 --> 42:39.765
to be crazy about each other
when you're both in love, okay?

42:41.517 --> 42:44.812
Really? You must be an expert in love.

42:44.937 --> 42:46.981
I'll keep that in mind and make use of it.

42:51.610 --> 42:53.696
Why do you keep being sarcastic?

42:53.779 --> 42:56.115
Who? Me?

42:58.450 --> 42:59.910
Even just now, you sounded sarcastic.

43:00.411 --> 43:01.662
You're wrong.

43:01.912 --> 43:02.788
You did it again.

43:09.878 --> 43:11.672
I apologize if I upset you.

43:12.840 --> 43:13.757
I'm sorry.

43:33.861 --> 43:34.945
It's raining.

43:38.907 --> 43:39.908
It is.

43:43.412 --> 43:44.788
It didn't say it was going to rain.

43:45.831 --> 43:46.999
Do you have an umbrella?

43:48.000 --> 43:48.917
No.

43:49.710 --> 43:51.378
I'll just go home in the rain.

43:51.754 --> 43:53.255
Why would you do that?

43:54.798 --> 43:57.009
You made me so angry
that I need to cool off.

44:00.929 --> 44:03.515
I already apologized. Cut me some slack.

44:07.311 --> 44:08.354
Fine.

44:11.774 --> 44:13.651
I'm the one who should be sorry.

44:13.734 --> 44:15.819
You couldn't eat that delicious pizza

44:15.903 --> 44:17.988
with Se-yeong because of me.

44:18.906 --> 44:21.784
It was out of my control,
so I hope you can forgive me.

44:23.744 --> 44:24.828
There's nothing to forgive.

44:25.329 --> 44:27.331
Let's just go together.
You'll come anyway, right?

44:27.414 --> 44:30.501
Why should I? I don't want to go
to a place where I'll feel unwelcome.

44:30.584 --> 44:31.669
Why would you feel that way?

44:31.960 --> 44:33.003
You don't get it, do you?

44:33.671 --> 44:35.673
Didn't you ask me
if I wanted to join you guys?

44:35.756 --> 44:37.925
You didn't say, "Let's go together."

44:39.551 --> 44:40.636
Did I ask you like that?

44:41.637 --> 44:44.014
I guess I didn't word it properly
because I was out of it.

44:44.098 --> 44:46.517
Right, I'm sure you were
totally out of it.

44:48.018 --> 44:49.061
Hey.

44:49.812 --> 44:52.564
Are looks all that matter to guys?

44:54.274 --> 44:55.275
I guess.

44:57.528 --> 44:58.987
Men are disgusting.

45:00.739 --> 45:01.573
You're prettier.

45:20.551 --> 45:21.593
This rain won't stop soon.

45:22.803 --> 45:24.388
Let's call a taxi.

45:25.097 --> 45:28.058
Then what about after you get off?
Wait here. I'll go buy an umbrella.

45:28.684 --> 45:29.810
Hey, let's just go...

45:57.337 --> 45:58.672
- How much is this?
- It's 8,000 won.

46:15.731 --> 46:16.940
What?

46:19.526 --> 46:20.360
Just come here.

46:28.994 --> 46:30.746
I thought you didn't want me to get wet.

46:30.871 --> 46:31.997
I got wet too.

46:32.122 --> 46:35.751
Gosh. By the way,
why did you just get one umbrella?

46:35.834 --> 46:37.002
And why red?

46:37.711 --> 46:40.881
Don't you know? Buying an umbrella
or a lighter is such a waste of money.

46:41.632 --> 46:43.091
I guess you'll become rich fast.

46:43.884 --> 46:46.803
But we'll both get soaking wet
if we share this umbrella like this.

46:47.304 --> 46:49.306
There's a solution for that.

46:49.723 --> 46:50.682
What?

46:51.099 --> 46:52.100
We can do this.

47:51.994 --> 47:53.495
Shall we take that taxi?

47:54.454 --> 47:55.455
Well...

47:55.998 --> 47:59.751
I think it'd be nice
to sober up a little first.

48:01.253 --> 48:02.254
Then...

48:02.504 --> 48:04.840
we should walk a bit more
before we get a taxi.

48:05.757 --> 48:06.800
Yes, I think so too.

48:17.811 --> 48:19.438
I didn't know you were this tiny.

48:19.938 --> 48:20.814
What?

48:21.815 --> 48:23.859
I didn't know
because you threw such a strong punch,

48:23.942 --> 48:26.945
- but you're so tiny.
- Hey, I'm not tiny.

48:27.029 --> 48:28.530
My height is average.

48:28.655 --> 48:30.157
Gosh, don't underestimate me.

48:30.407 --> 48:31.783
I know women well...

48:34.202 --> 48:35.787
Is that so?

48:37.039 --> 48:38.081
I was just kidding.

48:38.582 --> 48:39.499
Sure, whatever.

49:00.812 --> 49:02.397
Shall we watch a movie this weekend?

49:03.065 --> 49:05.567
I haven't been to the movies in ages.

49:06.652 --> 49:07.944
Isn't that what moms say?

49:08.487 --> 49:09.696
You little...

49:11.573 --> 49:12.658
Hey.

49:58.495 --> 49:59.788
It's getting late.

50:00.455 --> 50:01.540
You should get going.

50:02.207 --> 50:03.625
I'll go after I see you go in.

50:05.335 --> 50:07.587
You're using all your manners today.

50:09.381 --> 50:10.382
There's one more thing.

50:10.799 --> 50:11.800
What?

50:12.926 --> 50:14.302
It's a gift for you.

50:14.928 --> 50:16.596
But you bought it.

50:16.972 --> 50:19.099
That's why I'm calling it a gift. Here.

50:21.852 --> 50:23.270
Thank you.

50:28.233 --> 50:29.109
Go in.

50:29.651 --> 50:30.652
All right.

50:31.778 --> 50:33.155
Bye.

50:41.580 --> 50:43.623
- Get home safely.
- Sweet dreams.

50:44.750 --> 50:45.876
You, too.

52:26.142 --> 52:27.686
I'll give you three days.

52:28.311 --> 52:30.522
We'll have to close the store
if we don't hear from you.

52:52.210 --> 52:53.128
Hey.

52:53.628 --> 52:54.713
Are you at work now?

52:55.297 --> 52:57.382
No, not yet.
I had to stop by somewhere on the way.

52:57.591 --> 52:59.259
- What's up?
- Well...

52:59.342 --> 53:02.095
I'm craving a cup of coffee
brewed by an expert barista.

53:02.178 --> 53:05.181
Sir, you have to make
an appointment first.

53:05.265 --> 53:06.349
You're being so difficult.

53:06.892 --> 53:08.894
My time is expensive. Didn't you know?

53:09.102 --> 53:10.395
I guess you haven't sobered up.

53:10.854 --> 53:12.105
You wait right there.

53:29.748 --> 53:31.791
LAW FIRM

53:31.875 --> 53:32.876
Yes, sir.

53:36.713 --> 53:38.131
Yes, Father. Go ahead.

53:40.759 --> 53:41.760
No, it's okay.

53:41.843 --> 53:43.428
I'm just wondering

53:44.262 --> 53:46.598
if you have some time today.

53:47.474 --> 53:48.391
Yes.

53:49.726 --> 53:51.061
Tell him to come no matter what.

53:51.144 --> 53:53.897
My gosh, you must be busy
if you have taken on a big case.

53:55.148 --> 53:56.399
Of course, I understand.

53:57.442 --> 53:58.443
Yes.

53:59.819 --> 54:00.654
Really?

54:02.030 --> 54:03.281
All right, then.

54:03.531 --> 54:04.658
Okay.

54:06.451 --> 54:07.452
What did he say?

54:08.244 --> 54:09.871
I think he's extra busy these days.

54:09.955 --> 54:12.040
- Can he come or not?
- What?

54:12.749 --> 54:15.293
- He said he'd come.
- You're making me frustrated.

54:15.961 --> 54:18.964
Hang on, Seung-ho is coming too.
Is there enough meat for everyone?

54:20.006 --> 54:22.425
Shouldn't we tell Jin-a
that Gyu-min is coming?

54:22.509 --> 54:24.302
I'm sure they'll talk.

54:35.230 --> 54:36.398
I think you got a message.

54:38.024 --> 54:40.986
Se-yeong, shall we have that pizza today?

54:41.236 --> 54:43.905
Should I make a reservation
at the pizzeria for this evening?

54:44.197 --> 54:45.323
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

54:45.407 --> 54:46.992
Do you have plans for this evening?

54:48.952 --> 54:51.287
It's Jun-hui.
He wants to have that pizza today.

54:54.791 --> 54:57.043
Had I known about it,
I would have skipped lunch.

54:57.919 --> 54:59.963
I think I've gained
a bit of weight recently...

55:00.463 --> 55:02.465
I look like I've gained some weight,
don't I?

55:04.092 --> 55:06.428
I'm not sure.
I've never really paid much attention.

55:06.761 --> 55:08.221
I'm off.

55:14.686 --> 55:16.229
What are you doing this evening, Ye-eun?

55:16.312 --> 55:19.232
I have to redo the menu analysis
because it got rejected.

55:20.066 --> 55:22.569
You have to eat dinner though.
Let's go. I'll treat you.

55:23.319 --> 55:24.362
Really? Okay.

55:30.535 --> 55:32.245
Where should we go?

55:36.207 --> 55:37.834
A place that sells food and drinks.

55:39.294 --> 55:40.462
- Let's go.
- Okay.

55:46.926 --> 55:47.927
I should get going, then.

55:49.179 --> 55:50.305
Aren't you coming with us?

55:50.972 --> 55:52.432
- I have plans.
- He's going clubbing.

55:54.225 --> 55:55.226
You are?

55:55.435 --> 55:56.519
I like clubbing too.

55:56.603 --> 55:59.147
Oh, really?
We should all go together next time.

55:59.230 --> 56:00.356
I have something else today.

56:01.274 --> 56:04.110
All right, then.
Take us to a hip club next time.

56:04.444 --> 56:06.404
You can make other plans again next time.

56:06.488 --> 56:08.615
I'll keep that in mind.
Make sure she has a good time.

56:09.449 --> 56:10.950
I should do the same for him.

56:11.326 --> 56:13.161
- Shall we go?
- Let's go.

56:15.205 --> 56:16.331
I'll see you again soon.

56:28.426 --> 56:30.220
Seung-ho, are you there already?

56:47.695 --> 56:49.197
Is something wrong, Ms. Yoon?

56:50.031 --> 56:51.032
No.

56:51.950 --> 56:53.451
I just wanted to drink out of the blue.

56:56.830 --> 56:58.498
Do you still think about your ex a lot?

56:59.999 --> 57:02.460
You'll say that I'm lying
if I tell you that I don't.

57:04.129 --> 57:07.132
You have to meet someone new
to get over your ex-boyfriend.

57:07.423 --> 57:09.008
You should start seeing someone new.

57:12.220 --> 57:13.304
I'm good.

57:14.305 --> 57:17.100
Why? It's better to move on
to a new relationship as fast as possible.

57:17.767 --> 57:20.937
That way, you'll less likely
to repeat the same mistakes,

57:21.020 --> 57:22.522
which means you'll have fewer regrets.

57:22.605 --> 57:24.065
You sound like a pro.

57:24.941 --> 57:27.026
I may not have a lot of experience,

57:27.110 --> 57:28.570
but I know a lot about dating.

57:28.695 --> 57:30.113
I'm so proud of you.

57:32.240 --> 57:33.366
By the way,

57:34.534 --> 57:38.288
how much meaning should I put into
what a guy says or does to me?

57:39.998 --> 57:40.874
Pretty much none.

57:42.333 --> 57:43.334
None?

57:43.918 --> 57:47.547
"Hey, we can say anything and do
whatever it takes to seduce a girl."

57:47.714 --> 57:48.965
I'm an Engineering major.

57:49.090 --> 57:51.718
That's what I heard most often
from guys during college.

57:54.888 --> 57:58.766
But if a guy hits on a girl,

57:59.476 --> 58:01.144
doesn't it mean
that he's attracted to her?

58:01.895 --> 58:03.146
Well, I guess.

58:03.646 --> 58:06.483
But like my mom said,
guys don't say no to girls.

58:06.774 --> 58:09.444
I bet they flirt with every girl,
so they have options to choose from.

58:12.655 --> 58:13.948
Gosh.

58:17.869 --> 58:18.828
JERK GYU-MIN

58:21.372 --> 58:23.208
- I'll be right back. I have to take this.
- Sure.

58:26.211 --> 58:28.379
Hey, why the hell do you keep calling me?

58:28.463 --> 58:29.631
It's me, your dad.

58:30.298 --> 58:31.466
Dad?

58:32.300 --> 58:33.676
Why do you have Gyu-min's phone...

58:34.177 --> 58:35.803
Dad, are you with him now?

58:48.733 --> 58:50.652
I can't believe you bought
and brought these

58:50.735 --> 58:52.570
all the way from the States for me.

58:52.654 --> 58:54.155
Do you have trust issues or what?

58:54.906 --> 58:56.699
You've never gotten me any gifts before.

58:57.617 --> 59:01.371
Hey, are you sure you're smart enough
to get a PhD?

59:02.413 --> 59:04.332
This is my first time
coming back from the States.

59:04.415 --> 59:06.459
Oh, you're right.

59:07.710 --> 59:09.295
Gosh, your turn.

59:18.054 --> 59:21.307
Did you know that your sister and I
work in the same building?

59:22.141 --> 59:23.059
Really?

59:23.977 --> 59:25.061
You don't care about her?

59:27.146 --> 59:29.607
Do you care about everything
your sister is up to?

59:30.149 --> 59:31.401
Why would I?

59:32.735 --> 59:33.820
Then what?

59:34.988 --> 59:37.240
I was actually going to
invite you over to my place,

59:37.448 --> 59:39.200
but couldn't because of Jin-a's boyfriend.

59:44.080 --> 59:46.583
- Boyfriend?
- I guess you didn't know.

59:47.125 --> 59:49.794
There's a guy whom my mom adores so much.

59:50.795 --> 59:54.257
His educational background is impressive,
and his family is very rich.

59:57.176 --> 59:58.428
Are you saying he's coming over?

59:58.803 --> 01:00:00.263
Yes, he comes over often.

01:00:00.680 --> 01:00:03.641
I'm glad that I don't have to see him
often because I'm mostly at school.

01:00:04.142 --> 01:00:05.560
When those two are together...

01:00:06.603 --> 01:00:09.480
They make me want to barf.
It's such an eyesore.

01:00:15.570 --> 01:00:17.614
What the hell?

01:00:18.448 --> 01:00:19.824
I'm sorry.

01:00:19.907 --> 01:00:20.825
Hey.

01:00:22.160 --> 01:00:23.328
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

01:00:24.078 --> 01:00:25.204
What's with you?

01:00:27.332 --> 01:00:28.625
Gosh, what's your problem?

01:00:36.257 --> 01:00:37.342
Jin-a.

01:00:38.009 --> 01:00:40.053
Why are you standing there like that?

01:00:40.136 --> 01:00:43.473
Hey, Gyu-min got matching scarves

01:00:43.556 --> 01:00:45.391
for me and your dad.

01:00:45.475 --> 01:00:47.560
They look so nice.

01:00:47.644 --> 01:00:49.729
- Come and have a look.
- I need to get changed.

01:00:49.812 --> 01:00:50.855
Hey.

01:00:52.523 --> 01:00:55.693
Gyu-min, eat up. I made a lot of food.

01:01:01.866 --> 01:01:04.452
- I never asked you to do this!
- Shush. Keep your voice down!

01:01:06.204 --> 01:01:08.247
He told me everything.
He said you guys had a fight.

01:01:08.456 --> 01:01:09.582
That's what he told you?

01:01:10.875 --> 01:01:14.462
All couples have arguments and fights.

01:01:14.671 --> 01:01:17.465
He came all the way here to make up
with you. Why did you glare at him?

01:01:17.632 --> 01:01:20.343
Why do you keep getting crankier
as you get older?

01:01:21.636 --> 01:01:24.180
- Did you drink?
- How could I not drink?

01:01:24.639 --> 01:01:26.724
I can't cope with this when I'm sober.

01:01:27.308 --> 01:01:29.394
I'm old enough.
Why do you and Dad have to meddle--

01:01:29.477 --> 01:01:30.561
That's exactly why.

01:01:31.521 --> 01:01:34.315
Aren't you old enough to know
how to handle your man?

01:01:34.399 --> 01:01:35.733
You made us get involved.

01:01:36.442 --> 01:01:38.194
Aren't you embarrassed to see Gyu-min?

01:01:38.653 --> 01:01:39.946
Do better, okay?

01:01:40.947 --> 01:01:42.699
I've told you this numerous times.

01:01:42.782 --> 01:01:45.618
You won't be able to
date someone like him ever.

01:01:45.702 --> 01:01:47.995
He's a lawyer at a renowned law firm,

01:01:48.246 --> 01:01:49.414
not to mention his family.

01:01:49.664 --> 01:01:52.458
Both of his parents
are alumni of Seoul National University.

01:01:52.542 --> 01:01:55.378
I don't have to go on, do I?

01:01:56.254 --> 01:01:57.755
Choosing a good husband is important,

01:01:57.839 --> 01:02:00.675
and it's equally important
to have nice parents-in-law.

01:02:01.759 --> 01:02:04.637
Gyu-min is perfect in every aspect,

01:02:04.721 --> 01:02:06.723
and you should consider yourself
extremely lucky.

01:02:07.223 --> 01:02:08.933
You really should be grateful.

01:02:09.767 --> 01:02:11.394
You're so clueless.

01:02:13.187 --> 01:02:14.772
You'd better not grimace in front of him.

01:02:33.624 --> 01:02:35.501
- Goodbye.
- Thank you.

01:02:38.671 --> 01:02:39.839
Come to my home.

01:02:40.715 --> 01:02:43.384
- No, it's okay.
- Why not? Because of Jin-a's boyfriend?

01:02:43.926 --> 01:02:45.928
Who cares?
We'll hang out in my room anyway.

01:02:46.012 --> 01:02:47.305
I said, it's okay.

01:02:47.805 --> 01:02:50.600
But I do have to see your parents,
so let's pick another day.

01:02:51.601 --> 01:02:54.312
I was going to ask you
to install these games on my computer.

01:02:54.729 --> 01:02:56.272
I knew that was your plan, you idiot.

01:02:59.150 --> 01:02:59.984
Bye.

01:03:05.948 --> 01:03:06.949
Seung-ho!

01:03:12.663 --> 01:03:14.415
What's taking her so long?

01:03:15.708 --> 01:03:16.709
Oh, my.

01:03:18.169 --> 01:03:21.047
Mom and Dad,
there's no need to be surprised.

01:03:21.672 --> 01:03:24.801
I just thought that this might be
what Gyu-min wants.

01:03:26.719 --> 01:03:28.304
He told me that I'm like konjac.

01:03:28.930 --> 01:03:30.515
In other words, he thinks I'm too boring.

01:03:31.724 --> 01:03:35.394
Darling, why are you sitting like that?
Look at me.

01:03:35.520 --> 01:03:38.564
How do I look? Do you like this?

01:03:39.398 --> 01:03:40.525
Well?

01:03:42.360 --> 01:03:44.111
I guess even this isn't enough.

01:03:45.404 --> 01:03:48.324
Well, should I have worn a shorter dress?

01:03:48.950 --> 01:03:50.701
Should I have put on a redder lipstick?

01:03:51.577 --> 01:03:53.120
Right, fishnet stockings!

01:03:54.288 --> 01:03:56.749
- I don't own one, so I should rip this--
- Hey!

01:04:00.419 --> 01:04:03.256
Right, I forgot
that my parents are here too.

01:04:03.756 --> 01:04:06.175
That would be a little inappropriate,
right?

01:04:06.259 --> 01:04:08.803
Yes, just come and sit with us.

01:04:09.303 --> 01:04:10.513
Sit down, okay?

01:04:18.896 --> 01:04:22.441
I'm craving wine though.

01:04:27.029 --> 01:04:28.322
Aren't you seeing anyone?

01:04:30.533 --> 01:04:31.534
No.

01:04:31.617 --> 01:04:32.994
Really? That's so unlike you.

01:04:34.161 --> 01:04:35.413
Anyone you're interested in?

01:04:37.415 --> 01:04:40.042
You do have one.
Come on, tell me about her.

01:04:41.586 --> 01:04:42.712
What do you want to know?

01:04:44.255 --> 01:04:46.173
I guess things aren't going too well.

01:04:46.507 --> 01:04:47.508
Aren't I right?

01:04:48.175 --> 01:04:49.302
Are you a psychic or what?

01:04:49.552 --> 01:04:51.470
What's the problem? Who is she?
How old is she?

01:04:52.054 --> 01:04:53.639
Is she 23 or 24?

01:04:56.183 --> 01:04:57.184
She's 35.

01:04:59.186 --> 01:05:00.938
You nutjob. Have you lost your mind?

01:05:02.106 --> 01:05:04.483
You've gone nuts
since you got back from the States.

01:05:04.567 --> 01:05:05.818
Did you say she's 35?

01:05:07.820 --> 01:05:09.530
That means she's our sisters' age.

01:05:10.656 --> 01:05:12.199
How can you even be attracted to her?

01:05:13.159 --> 01:05:16.162
It's like you dating my sister.

01:05:16.537 --> 01:05:19.206
Gosh, I'm getting so creeped out.

01:05:19.790 --> 01:05:22.710
Hey, end it before things get serious.

01:05:22.793 --> 01:05:25.379
Don't end up in a total mess, okay?

01:05:44.273 --> 01:05:45.274
Mom.

01:05:46.817 --> 01:05:50.029
Did Dad ever cheat on you
when the two of you were dating?

01:05:50.529 --> 01:05:54.825
Gosh, come on.
What kind of person do you think I am?

01:05:55.576 --> 01:06:00.081
I have been and will always be devoted
to only one woman, Kim Mi-yeon.

01:06:03.542 --> 01:06:06.170
Devoted, my foot.
I even caught him red-handed.

01:06:07.171 --> 01:06:08.172
Seriously?

01:06:09.048 --> 01:06:12.051
Goodness, that was ages ago.

01:06:12.259 --> 01:06:15.763
So what did you do, Mom?
Did you let it slide?

01:06:15.846 --> 01:06:18.933
Of course not.
I gave him a good smack in the head.

01:06:22.269 --> 01:06:24.105
- Like this?
- That hurts.

01:06:24.271 --> 01:06:25.648
Hey!

01:06:26.899 --> 01:06:28.859
You should know when to draw the line.

01:06:29.151 --> 01:06:30.820
What was that about?

01:06:30.945 --> 01:06:33.572
Honey, be quiet.

01:06:34.615 --> 01:06:35.908
Gyu-min.

01:06:37.034 --> 01:06:38.160
Yes, Mother.

01:06:38.285 --> 01:06:39.996
You're seeing another woman, aren't you?

01:06:46.168 --> 01:06:48.629
I'm speechless.

01:06:48.713 --> 01:06:51.841
I didn't think you'd ever do such a thing.
I feel so betrayed.

01:06:52.591 --> 01:06:54.468
- How dare you...
- Honey!

01:06:56.929 --> 01:06:58.097
Gosh, Dad...

01:06:58.180 --> 01:06:59.306
- Please let go of me.
- Dad.

01:07:10.651 --> 01:07:11.736
He's probably still there.

01:07:12.903 --> 01:07:15.239
Gosh, those two must be
all over each other.

01:07:16.782 --> 01:07:17.908
Aren't your parents home?

01:07:18.784 --> 01:07:20.745
My parents encourage them.

01:07:32.965 --> 01:07:35.259
You're both adults.
Couldn't you have just talked to him?

01:07:35.342 --> 01:07:37.303
Gosh. Dear me.

01:07:37.386 --> 01:07:39.930
What is this mess? Gosh, seriously.

01:07:40.014 --> 01:07:41.766
- Why the hell are you pouting?
- Gosh.

01:07:41.849 --> 01:07:43.601
- Enough!
- You'll get hurt, Dad.

01:07:46.103 --> 01:07:49.273
I... I admit that I made a mistake.

01:07:50.066 --> 01:07:51.984
But Jin-a did it too. She cheated on me.

01:07:52.068 --> 01:07:53.444
She has another guy.

01:07:53.944 --> 01:07:54.779
Gyu-min!

01:07:54.862 --> 01:07:57.156
What? I'm not making anything up.

01:07:57.239 --> 01:08:00.034
Is this why you're here?
Are you here to cause a scene?

01:08:00.117 --> 01:08:01.952
Do you think it was easy
for me to come here?

01:08:02.078 --> 01:08:03.579
Then why did you come to begin with?

01:08:03.662 --> 01:08:06.165
Your parents invited me.
How could I say no?

01:08:06.290 --> 01:08:07.374
You should have said no.

01:08:08.250 --> 01:08:12.838
Had you had any respect
for me and my parents,

01:08:12.963 --> 01:08:14.799
you should've politely said no.

01:08:15.674 --> 01:08:18.594
Had I had more drinks, I wouldn't have
ended with just one smack--

01:08:18.677 --> 01:08:21.388
- Gosh, Jin-a. What is going on--
- Fine, go ahead and hit me.

01:08:21.472 --> 01:08:24.850
Punch me all you want if that will
make you feel better. Go ahead.

01:08:25.309 --> 01:08:26.310
You sound so desperate.

01:08:26.393 --> 01:08:28.187
I'm trying to patch things up here.

01:08:28.270 --> 01:08:30.272
- Let's start over and--
- Don't even think of it!

01:08:30.356 --> 01:08:32.108
That will never happen.

01:08:32.191 --> 01:08:34.318
Then do you really want
to break up with me?

01:08:35.111 --> 01:08:36.320
I thought we were through.

01:08:36.403 --> 01:08:38.739
Jin-a, what is happening?

01:08:40.032 --> 01:08:41.659
I'll explain everything later.

01:08:41.742 --> 01:08:44.078
Hey, why later? Tell them now.

01:08:45.788 --> 01:08:47.206
Shall we talk in front of them?

01:08:47.456 --> 01:08:50.668
Who's the prick
that picked you up from work?

01:08:50.751 --> 01:08:52.169
Who is he?

01:08:53.420 --> 01:08:56.382
You acted all faithful and made me
look like a douchebag who cheated on you.

01:08:56.465 --> 01:08:57.424
What about you?

01:08:59.343 --> 01:09:02.805
Does accusing me like that
make you feel better?

01:09:02.888 --> 01:09:05.891
Then why can't you tell me
who that guy is?

01:09:05.975 --> 01:09:07.935
You wouldn't hide it
if you did nothing wrong.

01:09:08.018 --> 01:09:10.813
I feel like I'm going crazy
because you're not telling me!

01:09:11.021 --> 01:09:12.314
I like him.

01:09:13.816 --> 01:09:14.817
Fine.

01:09:15.484 --> 01:09:17.153
I like him.
Do you have a problem with that?

01:09:17.236 --> 01:09:19.989
My gosh, I don't even know what to do now.

01:09:20.531 --> 01:09:21.740
I'm home.

01:09:21.824 --> 01:09:24.326
Seung-ho is home. What should we do?

01:09:24.660 --> 01:09:26.662
My gosh, Jun-hui.

01:09:26.954 --> 01:09:28.247
- Oh, gosh.
- What's wrong?

01:09:31.750 --> 01:09:32.918
What happened?

01:09:33.002 --> 01:09:34.128
Well, I'll explain--

01:09:34.211 --> 01:09:35.504
It's that guy.

01:09:36.964 --> 01:09:38.883
What are you talking about? Which guy?

01:09:39.592 --> 01:09:41.051
Who? You mean Jun-hui?

01:09:41.135 --> 01:09:42.386
You need to explain this.

01:09:50.352 --> 01:09:51.729
Let go of her hand.

01:09:52.271 --> 01:09:53.189
Hey.

01:09:56.901 --> 01:09:57.943
Follow me.

01:10:03.574 --> 01:10:05.326
- Break it up!
- Hey!

01:10:05.409 --> 01:10:07.453
- What's the matter with you?
- My goodness.

01:10:07.536 --> 01:10:09.246
- Hey, let go!
- Jun-hui!

01:10:09.330 --> 01:10:10.664
- Hey!
- What should we do?

01:10:10.748 --> 01:10:11.582
Hey!

01:10:28.390 --> 01:10:31.268
Jin-a likes him. She said it herself.

01:10:32.186 --> 01:10:33.312
- I heard you came by.
- Hey.

01:10:33.395 --> 01:10:35.272
I'm asking you if you came by to see me.

01:10:36.607 --> 01:10:37.983
You're so cute.

01:10:38.859 --> 01:10:40.736
Have you forgotten how old I am?

01:10:40.819 --> 01:10:44.240
- Doesn't that depend on the person?
- You little...

01:10:47.451 --> 01:10:49.078
Even relationships are all about timing.

01:10:49.161 --> 01:10:50.704
What if we keep missing the right time?

01:10:51.205 --> 01:10:52.623
I'd better make it move faster.

01:10:53.165 --> 01:10:54.208
I need to be bolder.

01:10:55.376 --> 01:10:56.877
Jin-a, I was just wondering...

01:10:57.878 --> 01:10:58.754
If...

01:10:59.421 --> 01:11:00.422
"If"?

01:11:00.506 --> 01:11:03.259
- If I ask you...
- Ask me what?

01:11:03.759 --> 01:11:05.094
If I ask you...

01:11:09.014 --> 01:11:10.683
to treat me to a meal tomorrow, would you?

01:11:15.271 --> 01:11:17.273
Subtitle translation by Lee Ja-won
